

  Deleting leading zeros 
 
  shift <field> left deleting leading '0'.                                    
  
  Placing leading zero
 
  You can use the function module
  'CONVERSION_EXIT_ALPHA_INPUT' and pass the fiel
  (or even part of the field) to be padded
  with zeroes.                          
 
  Or else, you can use WRITE field USING
  EDIT MASK '==ALPHA'.                    
 
  There is also a function module
  (conversion exit) '                            
 
  'CONVERSION_EXIT_ALPHA_OUTPUT' to do just the reverse.
 

